SUMMARY:Closure: WEST EALING STATION: Monday 29\, Tuesday 30 June and 
 Wednesday 1 July\, the station will close at 2252 each evening. Last 
 trains will call at 2235 (from Heathrow Terminal 4 to Abbey Wood) and 2250
  (from Abbey Wood to Heathrow Terminal 5). Please use local London Buses 
 services.
END:VEVENT
